{"tid":2314811,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【終於轉軚？】《華盛頓郵報》終於COVER返前幾日密西根州聽證會！！！！！！！","createTime":"2020-12-06T19:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T19:43:16.000Z","uid":88743,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0e692a9568a7995e603eb9fca2d9dcffa789acab","tid":2314811,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T19:24:18.000Z","msg":"轉軚？你以為啦<br />\n丑化緊班証人同朱利安尼咋咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jF3WtrPDmHU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjF3WtrPDmHU&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2ns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=b5f31940\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jF3WtrPDmHU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過識睇一定係睇留言同正負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nT N　1 hour ago<br />\nI wish I could watch this and find it humorous. Maybe after January 20, 2021. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nZina J　1 hour ago<br />\nKinda sad that they had to put a &quot;REALITY&quot; tag on some of the video clips. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nogEvanAlmighty　1 hour ago<br />\nYou guys cover SNL versions of events more than the actual events. An intelligent population would wonder why that is. <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nRabbit　1 hour ago<br />\nWitness affidavits are punishable in court if the person making claim is lying. There are signed affidavits affirming the accusations. They can be punished if there lying, so how is that different than being under oath? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦有美國人感到不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nRobert Landin　1 hour ago<br />\nIts over for 🇺🇸. This is so scary, its like a dystopian sci-fi movie. There will be blood and sorrow soon, look to your family. Stay safe. <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a2bbf48dd8d6a3147f57daa6b6493860e41f9f","tid":2314811,"uid":46151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T19:25:02.000Z","msg":"丑你老母"},{"pid":"88e2a1692c2bf55b14dfac6bd944c93527091345","tid":2314811,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"42a2bbf48dd8d6a3147f57daa6b6493860e41f9f","tid":2314811,"uid":46151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T19:25:02.000Z","msg":"丑你老母"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T19:28:25.000Z","msg":"正字點寫<br />\n唔記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我屌返你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2874bf9b1b480995eea798a757ce10ac6c9bde","tid":2314811,"uid":180429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"88e2a1692c2bf55b14dfac6bd944c93527091345","tid":2314811,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"42a2bbf48dd8d6a3147f57daa6b6493860e41f9f","tid":2314811,"uid":46151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T19:25:02.000Z","msg":"丑你老母"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T19:28:25.000Z","msg":"正字點寫<br />\n唔記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我屌返你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T19:30:11.000Z","msg":"醜啊"},{"pid":"7567c10c9417f040b2ba04800499f5c895eb6cb1","tid":2314811,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"88e2a1692c2bf55b14dfac6bd944c93527091345","tid":2314811,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"42a2bbf48dd8d6a3147f57daa6b6493860e41f9f","tid":2314811,"uid":46151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,